Life is a long and winding road.
It has unexpected
turns
hills
bumps
and other things.
Sometimes you have to make choices.
Which path?
Will you take the downhill or uphill?
left or right?
will you go back or go forward?
Sometimes you have to pay tolls.
Many times you see other cars fall into sinkholes.
but you have to make the choice of helping them, or going around it.

Sometimes you get turned down for something you really want.
You lose something thats very important to you.
That special thing you want leaves for the total opposite thing.
You lose that love that you hoped for.

You see someone struggling and you try to help.
But they don't want your help.
You come to understand that you can't help everyone

You can never change who somebody is, never.

But all in all you learn to accept it.
It's a fact of life.
And we move on.

Enjoy life to the fullest, and treasure every moment.
Every time you want what you can't have, you move on.

I love you all.  And this is my life.
